title: Darling, You Trend Me 11/5: Moose, Ashley Biden, Havana Syndrome, Aaron Rodgers, Pfizer, FBI
itunes:title: Darling, You Trend Me 11/5: Moose, Ashley Biden, Havana Syndrome, Aaron Rodgers, Pfizer, FBI
description:
In this edition of You Trend Me, Jack and special guest host Jamie Loftus discuss a moose barging into a Canadian classroom, Ashley Biden's journal ending up in the hands of Project Veritas, a Havana Syndrome update, Aaron Rodgers being 'in the crosshairs of the woke mob', Pfizer's new experimental anti-viral drug, and the FBI tapes that show white supremacists plotting a race war.
